I am now going to pass my poor clicking

00:40:31.350 --> 00:40:34.440
off to Clarissa who's going to tell you

00:40:34.440 --> 00:40:38.503
more about the Toolkit itself
and give you a tour and ...

00:40:42.050 --> 00:40:45.500
- So here it is. Use it. (laughs)

00:40:45.500 --> 00:40:46.593
Take a picture.

00:40:49.050 --> 00:40:52.930
There's a sample of an
accommodation letter.

00:40:52.930 --> 00:40:54.110
There's a couple samples of

00:40:54.110 --> 00:40:56.540
accommodation letters in your packet

00:40:56.540 --> 00:40:59.140
so you can see what that
